<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99487136341098></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99487136341098><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=6&mid=99487136341098>RE: 2HS</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=6&mid=99487136341098#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jul 11th 1:09 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Torsk,<br><br>I had the same problem before.&nbsp;&nbsp;I had an ACG and with the damage ratio and stats, it seemed like a decent enuff weapon even with out fbss.  Damage-wise that is.  ORB, fast even with out fbss, but heck of a lot faster with haste.  Now to your DN weapon that you sold.  Velium Battle axe is a good weapon even with out stats.  <br>See, the thing that we do best is taunt.  I currently weild a Velium Claidhmore put that together with both stun and holy might, that mob will be permanently on your ass. With my mith2hs at level 40, although fast and decent damage, it wasnt high enuff to taunt with, although i was still taunting well enuff.  <br><br>IMHO, I would have sold orb and acg and kept your rare DN weapon.  Any Dragon Necropolis weapon that we can weild is hard to beat.  Specially if your grouped with a Chanter(best haste) and a Shaman(buffs) most of the time.  Stats that you do get from your weapon is nice to have specially with xp groups, but if you go to raids, you'll get buffed out so much that every tank seems to have at least 3000hp and over 1000ac and with Clarity 2 anyway hehehe. <br>Either way you win!<br><br>This is just my opinion.<br><br>All things considered,  its hard to screw up on which ever way you go.  Bottomline, you had the options that many paladins at your level didnt have.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
